summary: Kygarra and vaalsark CBBE version, (textures only).
descriptionHtml:
Hi, This is my re-texture of the Kygarra and Vaalsark race for CBBE bodyes.

I use to do textures for myself, but since aren't any new textures to these races so here's mine.I use CBBE HDT but it should work with any CBBE body.
There's an alternative FOX texture version if u want to play as a  Lilmothiit (http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/73521).

U need the original mods to be installed first, then overwrite the texture files from this mode (Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\Skyrim\Data\textures\actors\Character\...)

Vaalsark: www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13561

Kygarra: www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/61555
author: Wolf of the azar
